      "summary": "Vapi on the homepage plus Telnyx call routing — answer, qualify, hand off, or book.",
      "features": [
        {
          "id": "voice-routing",
          "title": "Call path",
          "body": "Inbound voice hits an AI agent that greets, qualifies, and routes — to a human, SMS, email, or the calendar.",
